Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不起床的話要遲到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說海君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.82,0:00:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該決定志願了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢的事情不用擔心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.83,0:00:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君做想做的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.61,0:01:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 吃相太壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天會晚回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯你自己先吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.86,0:01:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是最後的暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何別留下遺憾好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.85,0:01:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君也要小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.57,0:02:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:40.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻先で揺れる残り香消すように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:47.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足早に過ぎてゆく夏の風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:56.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服のボタンも少しだけこすれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:03.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通りのベンチさえも時を刻んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:11.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あの夏は今も僕らを待っているかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:21.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振り返る君の笑顔 焼き付けたフィルムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れない…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:28.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束も 駆け抜ける潮騒も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:36.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火が写した仲間と笑う一瞬さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薄れない愛しさも 遠くなる思い出も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこかで待ってる季節へのエンドロール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:52.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャッターを開いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘れない…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:13.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束も 駆け抜ける潮騒も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:21.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花火が写した仲間と笑う一瞬さえも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:28.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バラバラの僕たちの思い出も
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:33.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どこかで待ってる未来へjoint-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:39.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,フィルムを繋いで…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.24,0:02:40.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是鼻尖飄過的一絲香氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:47.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天的風快步地吹過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:56.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校服上的紐扣 也擦到了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:03.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路邊的長椅 也留下了時光的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.44,0:03:11.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天 如今仍然在等待我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:21.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回眸一笑的情景 已然印在膠片中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:22.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會忘記…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:28.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的約定 洶涌的海潮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:36.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以煙花為背景與夥伴們一起歡笑的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.55,0:03:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不褪色的喜愛 日漸遙遠的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:48.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通向那個等待著我們的季節的end-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:52.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開快門…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不會忘記…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:13.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的約定 洶涌的海潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:21.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以煙花為背景與夥伴們一起歡笑的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼想實現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:28.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們每個人的回憶片段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:33.71,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是通向未來的joint-roll
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:39.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手上的膠片接起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…慾求不滿麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給應該在寶貴的暑假期間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力學習的海人君帶來慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過散漫得似乎完全不需要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息啦 休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 殺必死時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪來的大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢 今天什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柑菜讓我來看看阿海你有沒有好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊 沒一點信任
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別偷懶好好學習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不懂就跟我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼可讓你教的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家裏做的話 老姐會嫌很難聞什麼的諸多意見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美姐又回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已經是病了 治不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.93,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿聰這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她老公很忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說外星人相關是頂級機密什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼問也不透露一點口風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北原呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說今天柑菜會去她家住下一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生之間的秘密會議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容的話多少能猜到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢騷啦 牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎的包裏有情書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且有三封
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下之前先給我拒絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎愛裝酷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來呢後來呢 情書怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是當場撕掉扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太狠了吧美櫻同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不狠一點 阿哲是不會明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲一直都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是考慮對方的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不表達自己的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 美櫻 唔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看美櫻 烤爐預熱好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}雖然我也知道他很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}但總該有好好擺明自己態度的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一個月前被他姐姐叫出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北原的心情我也能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你沒對大家說你們在交往啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那個怎麼說來著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.73,0:08:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點小難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說啥啊 該做的事都做過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別弄太亂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.18,0:08:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是阿海說了奇怪的話吧 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底誰才是猥瑣大叔啊 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.55,0:08:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.18,0:08:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 坐墊下面找到了這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠片卷盤？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼會在這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來之前整理過膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼時候的膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是拍電影之前試拍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 哲郎個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是公開好好說明啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:18.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓美櫻那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去死 先殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 都說了那封信不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像跟偶像信差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬人迷就是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說喜歡我就不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超 超愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服的澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我也是說過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}阿哲的心意我是知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}今天去過霧島君家了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像不鬧情緒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了8毫米的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在霧島君家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.59,0:10:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8毫米是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柑菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉在那裏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍電影之前說試拍什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家聚在阿海家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上玩煙花的時候拍過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說起來是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼又翻出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是整理膠片的時候拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後忘記收回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柑菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海人君 現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:17.69,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,294)}我們在高中最後的夏天 等待著那個夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.36,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐明天要早起就先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了很懷念的膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天不叫你起床了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.92,0:12:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 已經在拍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼在意就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平常一樣就行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是有點難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的啦 貴月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是測試
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會用在正片裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也放鬆不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿海 反光板像這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 石垣君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎 你在搞什麼攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請 請問
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 只要慢慢走過來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出點環顧周圍景色的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右手和右腳一起出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這電影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.03,0:13:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這次就改下曝光度再拍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們從原來的地方重新來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柑菜 剛才為止拍了多少了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多正好一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3分鐘還挺長的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說阿海 這樣真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市花學姐的演技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.19,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話就是連外行都不如
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是第一次嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.27,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾天後就要開始拍攝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船到橋頭自然直吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.47,0:14:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持自然真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.95,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都緊張得口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.54,0:14:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再來一杯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這麼神出鬼沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐 劇本完成了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了寫出更完美的劇本
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算好好觀察扮演女主角的市花以激發靈感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒寫好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看著市花學姐那演技也想不出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嫵媚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.95,0:15:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只差2歲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼有這麼大差別
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿海 攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要拍嗎 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體發熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人有點奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}等下美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.01,0:16:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好痛 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}眼鏡壓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.73,0:16:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}話說前面都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 拍攝到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為什麼 就是不拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在生什麼氣呢 谷川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼 又不是在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.53,0:16:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 都是因為學姐有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 變得很奇怪的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷川同學 害羞的表情被拍到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.95,0:16:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 靈感像開水一樣涌出來根本停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在這裏睡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:16:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像安穩地睡了 現在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺態度突然就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是不習慣拍攝累著了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是拍了一點而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子還能拍什麼電影嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 市花是個說做就一定做到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧島君你能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試複習的時候深刻體會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你跟貴月學姐發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒什麼 兩人一起學習到半夜而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣被學姐教了很多事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有像戀愛故事那樣在浴室來個心跳情景什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊真沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼啊 阿海和學姐兩人一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過了一個月都沒有發生什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒骨氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說還是說說電影的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得大家都在場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才就一聲不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都不像沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北原…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 好了 回到原來的話題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 要說回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.89,0:18:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒跟貴月學生發生什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回到那麼前嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 想矇混過去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別纏人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}什麼都沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣……才叫纏人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄權 棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谷川 我棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸 胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…也碰到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵 大家都好棒 呵呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我買來了好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了 大家都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙花買過來了 然後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還挺有勁頭的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎 給我火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿哲燒完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我來拿下個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海君 這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放出來什麼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.13,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好 接下來兩個一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.40,0:21:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.99,0:21:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都笑著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.02,0:22:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲郎 北原 谷川 檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.32,0:22:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有市花學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.30,0:22:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拍到谷川的肚臍眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.28,0:22:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上給我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.26,0:22:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.70,0:22:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 我也要玩更好看的 來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.13,0:22:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是能拿在手上的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}來 拿這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}好啦 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說美櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.06,0:22:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然還是要去東京的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.94,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.99,0:23:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.20,0:23:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來還想再拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.31,0:23:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓人叫好的happy end的電影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們成長的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.23,0:23:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}好 剩下來的也大玩一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那我要這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}那我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棱角都慢慢變得模糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.25,0:23:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人焦躁 讓人痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.86,0:23:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次看到留下的膠片
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就會這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 如果沒有遇到學姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.71,0:24:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.96,0:24:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定活得跟現在不同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.67,0:24:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這不是結束
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.84,0:24:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在繼續著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.85,0:24:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在等待著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.72,0:24:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映在膠片上的……
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:24:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天的……
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.21,0:25:06.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結尾字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:22.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消えた 花火の後は
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:30.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦い火薬の香り
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:34.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燻る視界の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.87,0:25:44.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同じ高さの君の視線を見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:59.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたり同時に はにかんだりしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.46,0:26:03.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはただがむしゃらに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.93,0:26:11.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不器用な言葉で 未来を探して
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.45,0:26:16.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫りくる衝動を抱え込む
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:25.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもなく幸せな結末を望んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:32.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眩しい あの夏の日
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.35,0:25:22.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熄滅的煙花 留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.77,0:25:30.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點苦的火藥香味
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.29,0:25:34.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙熏的視界前方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.87,0:25:44.59,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到了你在同一水平的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.69,0:25:59.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果你我雙方 同時害羞起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.46,0:26:03.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一心忘我地
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.93,0:26:11.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不成熟的言語 去探尋未來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.45,0:26:16.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱洶涌而至的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.63,0:26:25.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渴望一個完美的幸福結局
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:32.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天的時光 是如此的耀眼

